('7f91550e-8b41-5de3-bbb2-8ba6e1948e84', '056bbf79-2f62-44e1-88e9-19e796ece41a', 'The company ___ launch a new product line to compete with its rivals next month.', '這間公司將於下個月推出新產品線以與競爭對手競爭。', 'will', 'must', 'can', 'may', '助動詞，用於表示未來或計畫。', 'will → 將會 (助動詞用法)');
